short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find adoptable dogs near you, using the PetFinder database

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Our Rescue Dawg extension helps you find lovely adoptable rescue dogs near you. Simply enter your zipcode and the extension will search through the whole PetFinder database for your match.
Some listings have photos, while others don't but in all cases you will be able to contact the rescue center for more information.
